{"tid":1598463,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"★ipad/iphone直駁usb drive醜態圖！！","createTime":"2019-09-27T12:54:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-28T15:28:26.000Z","uid":19454,"like":12,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f664f230d92127e37e7baf7905c7086a2d3e75bc","tid":1598463,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T12:54:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://mrmad.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/ipad-ipados-usb-link-power-2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmrmad.com.tw%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F06%2Fipad-ipados-usb-link-power-2.jpg&h=bd548c79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db7596a8ccb46839f3021b26cad9afe852f318de","tid":1598463,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T12:56:14.000Z","msg":"iPad 和 iPhone 讀取 USB 隨身碟支援度測試，實測 iOS 13、iPadOS 支援格式<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://mrmad.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/ipados-and-ios13-read-the-usb-flash-drive-test.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmrmad.com.tw%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F06%2Fipados-and-ios13-read-the-usb-flash-drive-test.jpg&h=eaa99c2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n還在煩惱要買 USB-C 款 iPad Pro 才能夠支援 USB 隨身碟讀取？其實並不需要，在瘋先生測試手邊 iPhone 和舊款 9.7吋 iPad Pro 全升級至 iOS 13 和 iPadOS 新系統，證實都已經可以支援讀取寫入 USB 隨身碟和外接硬碟 ，也不一定要購買 USB-C 款 iPad Pro 才能夠支援。<br />\n<br />\n也就是說 Lightning 設備同樣只要升級到新系統，也可以讀寫 USB 隨身碟或硬碟內資料，但是讀取的連結設備要怎麼買才對呢？要先確認你是要用在 iPhone 和 iPad 上面，並且確認設備充電孔即可。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\nLightning 設備<br />\n如果是 Lightning 接口設備，像是 iPhone 或 iPad，就需要透過蘋果官網購買「 Lightning 對 USB 3 相機轉接器」，售價NT$1,190，千萬不要買「Lightning 對 USB 相機轉接器」單頭那款，會導致USB 3.0 隨身碟電壓不足，造成沒辦法讀取，就需要依賴透過另一孔藉由 Lightning to USB 傳輸線供電，這款轉接頭門市很少貨，只能到官網下單訂購，估計這篇出來也會導致台灣經銷商全面鋪貨吧？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://mrmad.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/Lightning-to-USB3-Camera-Adapter.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmrmad.com.tw%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F06%2FLightning-to-USB3-Camera-Adapter.jpg&h=aafefa40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nUSB-C 設備<br />\n蘋果替 iPad Pro 改採用 USB-C 其實是有道理，因為 Lightning 面臨供電不足，反而 USB-C 可以克服 USB 3.0或外接硬碟供電不足問題。至於 USB-C 轉接頭挑選，可直接買「USB-C 對 USB 轉接器」NT$590，或是其他有認證過的 USB-C ，像是 亞果元素CASA Hub A08 \b會是不錯選擇。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n實測 iPad 讀取 USB 連接法<br />\n本篇以 Lightning 接口的 9.7吋 iPad Pro 為例子，iPhone 也是採用同樣方法；將 Lightning 對 USB 3 相機轉接器接上設備，並將 USB 隨身碟插上轉接器。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://mrmad.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/ipad-ipados-usb-link-power-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmrmad.com.tw%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F06%2Fipad-ipados-usb-link-power-1.jpg&h=33db8b9a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"105395d1b4a3021cf0c8c1fd9474a68d4d329911","tid":1598463,"uid":8410,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T12:56:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咪同佢d macbook 一樣， 駁舊大大舊的adaptor"},{"pid":"3fc58ae49119be50dc79a61dfd9dcedf82e51c75","tid":1598463,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T12:57:10.000Z","msg":"要是 USB 3.0 隨身碟供電不足，會直接跳出「Ultra USB 3.0: This accessory requires too much power.」，表示需要另外接上電源線才能讓 USB 隨身碟讀取。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://mrmad.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/ipados-and-ios13-read-the-usb-flash-drive-test-10.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmrmad.com.tw%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F06%2Fipados-and-ios13-read-the-usb-flash-drive-test-10.jpg&h=d225eed3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n此時，就需要透過另一條 Lightning 對 USB 傳輸線連接才能供電，除了透過電源頭外，也可以接上電腦供電。（圖片內採用的是 OMNIA P5 電源器 ，可通吃通QC和PD快充）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://mrmad.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/ipad-ipados-usb-link-power-2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmrmad.com.tw%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F06%2Fipad-ipados-usb-link-power-2.jpg&h=bd548c79&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"824d051575a5e9ab2c59facb69519bdef9b72a06","tid":1598463,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T12:58:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">小心少數冷門 USB 無法支援</span><br />\n大家應該聽過光碟機會挑片對吧？但 iPad 和 iPhone 可是也會挑隨身碟的喔！<br />\n<br />\n手邊測試過創見 Transcend、SanDisk 隨身碟都是可以正常讀取，就唯獨 TDK 隨身碟是無法讀取，會直接跳出「Cannot Use Accessory」錯誤，就算格式化成可相容的格式，同樣還是無法讀取，所以挑選 USB 盡量選擇大廠牌，避免遇到 iPad 無法讀取問題。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://mrmad.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/ipados-and-ios13-read-the-usb-flash-drive-test-11.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmrmad.com.tw%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F06%2Fipados-and-ios13-read-the-usb-flash-drive-test-11.jpg&h=1e8fee4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">配件驅動更新</span><br />\n首次接上轉接器後，會跳出有可用的配件更新，問你要求更新 Apple USB Camera Adapter 嗎？點擊「更新」繼續。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://mrmad.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/ipados-and-ios13-read-the-usb-flash-drive-test-2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmrmad.com.tw%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F06%2Fipados-and-ios13-read-the-usb-flash-drive-test-2.jpg&h=deaed0fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n接下來等待更新完成即可，這個更新估計也是用來防堵山寨版破解傳輸線更新，如果沒有更新估計也是無法讀取 USB 內資料。<br />\n<br />\n[img]<a href=\"https://mrmad.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/ipados-and-ios13-read-the-usb-flash-drive-test-1.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmrmad.com.tw%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F06%2Fipados-and-ios13-read-the-usb-flash-drive-test-1.jpg&d=MLRnjlmMEh1el5UvTt2rHa9osQ3F9Lpm1EhhEwxE9Bk%3D&h=e1c04df6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mrmad.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/ipados-and-ios13-read-the-usb-flash-drive-test-1.jpg</a><br />\n[/img]"},{"pid":"2c3bfe2eda32a49e29be82200bfbe9f1100601fa","tid":1598463,"uid":5159,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T12:58:57.000Z","msg":"繼我話用android"},{"pid":"a831c0f96b0e0f0a9dfa357abb7efbc549fd91eb","tid":1598463,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T12:59:32.000Z","msg":"USB 格式支援相容度<br />\n應該不少人好奇有哪些 USB 格式是能夠支援 iPad 和 iPhone 讀取和寫入？目前測試除了 NTFS 格式無法讀取和寫入外，其他使用 FAT32、ExFAT、 APFS 都是能支援讀取與寫入，你沒看錯 FAT32 也可以支援，蘋果佛心爆發了嗎？<br />\n<br />\nUSB 格式 讀取 寫入<br />\n        FAT32 ✅ ✅<br />\n        ExFAT ✅ ✅<br />\n        NTFS ❌ ❌<br />\nMac OS 擴充格式（APFS） ✅ ✅"},{"pid":"487ee253cbbdad795947232eb0f9dd5e2d37a115","tid":1598463,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T13:00:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">如何透過 iPad 將資料放進 USB 內？</span><br />\n可別認為透過 Safari 下載後的檔案可以存到外接 USB 內，需要先將檔案存在 iPad 硬碟內，再透過搬移方式複製到 USB 內。但是 AirDrop是可以先透過檔案開啟後，再轉存至 USB 內，其實還蠻方便的。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但\b測試時發現個小問題，唯獨 APFS 格式隨身碟 ，可將 iPad 本機裝置或 iCloud Drive 檔案，透過「複製」再到USB「貼上」 ，反而其他格式，就只能透過「搬移」&gt;「拷貝」到 USB 上才能實現複製。估計這是一個 Bug 功能，但至少可實現寫入到 USB 檔案的功能。"},{"pid":"dbc35b75580a6fd6e41fff175a881e643d24ddda","tid":1598463,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T13:01:04.000Z","msg":"too long<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://mrmad.com.tw/ipados-and-ios13-read-the-usb-flash-drive-test\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmrmad.com.tw%2Fipados-and-ios13-read-the-usb-flash-drive-test&d=MLRnjlmMEh1el5UvTt2rHa9osQ3F9Lpm1EhhEwxE9Bk%3D&h=7239d4be\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mrmad.com.tw/ipados-and-ios13-read-the-usb-flash-drive-test</a>"},{"pid":"599c430f99e30c0576ae64bfa46e833c609ba7cc","tid":1598463,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a831c0f96b0e0f0a9dfa357abb7efbc549fd91eb","tid":1598463,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T12:59:32.000Z","msg":"USB 格式支援相容度<br />\n應該不少人好奇有哪些 USB 格式是能夠支援 iPad 和 iPhone 讀取和寫入？目前測試除了 NTFS 格式無法讀取和寫入外，其他使用 FAT32、ExFAT、 APFS 都是能支援讀取與寫入，你沒看錯 FAT32 也可以支援，蘋果佛心爆發了嗎？<br />\n<br />\nUSB 格式 讀取 寫入<br />\n        FAT32 ✅ ✅<br />\n        ExFAT ✅ ✅<br />\n        NTFS ❌ ❌<br />\nMac OS 擴充格式（APFS） ✅ ✅"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T13:03:00.000Z","msg":"no ntfs=rubbish"},{"pid":"752292af7567b2e645980c71a2119339a88a41e4","tid":1598463,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T13:04:33.000Z","msg":"gay cook love Jer Style<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39ff5ebbfed54b7f063e99fa27f6db8fc98d3a05","tid":1598463,"uid":5159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T13:04:43.000Z","msg":"點解咁多年都未有格式取代到 ntfs"},{"pid":"a2b0cc76d6a5e4d18a6ad544f5fa544c3bf71e06","tid":1598463,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"752292af7567b2e645980c71a2119339a88a41e4","tid":1598463,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T13:04:33.000Z","msg":"gay cook love Jer Style<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T13:05:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://mrmad.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/ipad-ipados-usb-link-power-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmrmad.com.tw%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F06%2Fipad-ipados-usb-link-power-1.jpg&h=33db8b9a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bcdfef4b7aea4728185aeadc701506d259b699ff","tid":1598463,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T13:08:53.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"06ca41e955df1f8267a24feabda1a3afa96d3a99","tid":1598463,"uid":1130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"39ff5ebbfed54b7f063e99fa27f6db8fc98d3a0