xFAT ✅ ✅<br />\n        NTFS ❌ ❌<br />\nMac OS 擴充格式（APFS） ✅ ✅"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T13:03:00.000Z","msg":"no ntfs=rubbish"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T15:28:26.000Z","msg":"隻手指有套6G AV（NTFS)已經播不到<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}